settings.description: The sewers have been filled with water, possibly too much to handle for Mario.

I'm sure every level set needs an underwater stage! And where there is water, there is bound to be a frog somewhere in it!
Difficulty: 4/5
Climb up inside a volcano and go digging for Ace Coins!  Watch out, it's hot!
The destroyed constructions were destroyed by the boss bass before the level,enjoy.
Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!
It's all just Tetriminos in this wacky world.
waterfalls, koopas, ptooies, and a incredible view of a nice sunset! what more can you ask for minus a hidden hammer suit?~
